00:02:09.460 --> 00:02:15.490
As a Colombian poet and novelist
Mutis was often overshadowed

00:02:15.490 --> 00:02:18.980
by his friend and compatriot,
Gabriel Garcia Marquez.

00:02:18.980 --> 00:02:22.130
