00:52:00.400 --> 00:52:04.730
&gt;&gt; What was his personal life like?

00:52:04.730 --> 00:52:06.030
&gt;&gt; Charlotte Rogers:
Well, I mean I know

00:52:06.030 --> 00:52:08.610
